'''Antonín Absolon''' is a retired [[Czechoslovakia|Czechoslovak]] [[slalom canoeing|slalom canoeist]] who competed in the mid-to-late 1960s. He won a silver medal in the mixed C-2 team event at the [[1965 ICF Canoe Slalom World Championships]] in [[Spittal an der Drau|Spittal]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Overview of athlete's results|website=CanoeSlalom.net |url=http://www.canoeslalom.net/int/index/index_65.html#2400 |accessdate=30 August 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904025927/http://www.canoeslalom.net/int/index/index_65.html#2400 |archivedate=4 September 2014 }}</ref>

